{"tid":884021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樓市點睇：陳永傑估下月繼續跌　中原年底裁員","createTime":"2018-10-31T09:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T09:37:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc54023c8d8c5920ecc61147eac6a74fba55a7d6","tid":884021,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T09:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181031/photo/bkn-20181031170851562-1031_00842_001_01p.jpg?20181031172732\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181031170851562-1031_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20181031172732&h=4d9ec702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n差估署樓價指數連跌兩個月，中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑認為，由於該數字較實際情況滯後，估計下個月公布會再下跌。他認為，受中美貿易戰及市場進入加息周期影響，導致市況波動的情況，預計要待外圍因素穩定，樓價才會較平穩。 <br />\n<br />\n他又表示，住宅樓市交投不多，集團未來會開源節流，鼓勵員工涉獵工商物業買賣，而年底將進行節流行動，裁減未達指標的員工，坦言「依個行業係要孭quota」。 <br />\n<br />\n他又透露，現時集團每月有約150至200人自然流失，估計未來將會更多，但人事部會不斷增聘人手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181031/bkn-20181031170851562-1031_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181031%2Fbkn-20181031170851562-1031_00842_001.html&d=FwYAA6jDIqA0QZLQKYkRCsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=56168de6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181031/bkn-20181031170851562-1031_00842_001.html</a>"}]}